                        <h2>What we can offer</h2>
                        <p class="leadd">Users will be able to login and create/view/edit/delete projects, as well as tasks within a project. Projects can have multiple users, a many-to-many relationship that will allow users to work on teams. Crucially, the task model will be hierarchical, so large project layouts can be created with many hierarchical layers of “sub-tasks”. <br>
                         <p class="leadd">This is a useful paradigm when combined with the front-end, which will employ the D3.js library to render an interactive infographic based on packed circles. With this interface, users will be able to view the entire status of their project at a glance.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
